                            <comment id="481970" author="adilger" created="Sat, 20 Dec 2025 10:08:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Is there possibly a test-framework or sanity-sec patch that landed recently that is trying to drop DLM locks after the file system is unmounted?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
